- Bu..

00:04:45.767 --> 00:04:46.890
Jangan khawatir.

00:04:47.725 --> 00:04:48.809
Sai benar-benar baik-baik saja.

00:04:49.600 --> 00:04:51.392
Bagaimana dia bisa baik-baik
saja tanpa makan apapun?

00:04:52.350 --> 00:04:53.350
Dia tidak kelaparan.

00:04:54.642 --> 00:04:56.642
Dia menikmati 'Kanda Poha'.

00:04:57.767 --> 00:04:58.809
Bagaimana Anda tahu bahwa?

