..hatimu keluar.  - Oke.

00:18:34.414 --> 00:18:35.749
Anda menyukai orang yang jujur.

00:18:36.744 --> 00:18:37.744
Kamu benci pembohong.

00:18:38.613 --> 00:18:39.613
Dan..

00:18:41.533 --> 00:18:42.867
Anda suka bepergian.

00:18:43.598 --> 00:18:44.598
Musik..

00:18:47.257 --> 00:18:49.257
Dan Anda suka mencari teman baru.

00:18:50.883 --> 00:18:51.672
Tuhan.

00:18:52.944 --> 00:18:54.547
Benar Anda menebak.

00:18:55.492 --> 00:18:56.492
Satu hal lagi.

